Ss0YgWYKvI3dxEIoLexQeJ7ZsbRU6Q7TtdkGJJik"},{"type":"url","url":"https://alliswellspa.com/"}]}},{"id":"tco_2ccb4588-b386-96cf-b876-55306819d796_call-727c1176-bcec-4866-a3b4-f2dc0a7d7f78-0","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_2ccb4588-b386-96cf-b876-55306819d796_call-727c1176-bcec-4866-a3b4-f2dc0a7d7f78-1","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_2ccb4588-b386-96cf-b876-55306819d796_call-727c1176-bcec-4866-a3b4-f2dc0a7d7f78-2","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"**Top-rated skincare spas in Katy, Texas, based on recent Yelp reviews and other mentions (as of mid-2026 data), emphasize facials, skin treatments, and medspa services.** Ratings focus on customer feedback for skincare-specific services like facials, peels, and esthetics.[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\nHere are some of the highest-rated options:\n\n- **Face to Face Spa**: Frequently ranks near the top with a strong **4.9/5 rating** (around 35 reviews). It appears in multiple \"best facials\" lists for personalized skincare.[[2]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facials&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\n- **Facials by Jada**: Consistently #1 or #2 on Yelp facial searches with **4.8/5** (30 reviews). Specializes in facials, skincare, waxing, and lashes; praised for expertise and results.[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\n- **Divinity Spa**: **4.8/5** (31 reviews) and often listed in top facial/spa categories for quality treatments.[[2]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facials&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\n- **Wellness Spa - Katy**: **4.5/5** (40–41 reviews). A popular choice for massages, medical spa services, and skincare; appears frequently in \"best skin care\" and facial lists.[[3]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Skin+Care&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\n- **MedSpa at Villagio**: Noted for volume of reviews (over 100 in some lists) and awards (two-time Image Skincare Medspa of the Year). Offers medical-grade facials, peels, lasers, and full beauty services in a day-spa setting.[[4]](https://medspaatvillagio.com/)\n\nOther notable mentions include **SkinSpirit Katy** (premier medspa for facials, Botox, and fillers), **Spavia Cinco Ranch** (luxury day spa with facials and body treatments), **Anita’s Skin Care Clinic** (custom facials, peels, and holistic options), and **All Is Well Massage & Spa** (holistic/organic skincare focus).[[5]](https://www.skinspirit.com/locations/katy)\n\n**Tips**: Check current Yelp, Google, or the spas’ websites for the latest reviews, availability, and specifics (e.g., medical vs. traditional spa). Many offer packages or consultations—ratings can shift with new reviews. For the most personalized experience, read recent client feedback on skincare results. Locations are concentrated in areas like Cinco Ranch and near Katy Mills.","logprobs":[],"annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":273,"end_index":344,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":344,"end_index":415,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facials&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":638,"end_index":710,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":898,"end_index":969,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facials&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":1083,"end_index":1155,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Skin+Care&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":1334,"end_index":1408,"title":"3"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://medspaatvillagio.com/","start_index":163